WEBSTER'S
INTERNATIONAL
DICTIONARY.  2348 PAGES.      5000 ILLUSTRATIONS.   NEW EDITION, REVISED THROUGHOUT WITH A NEW SUPPLEMENT OF 25,000 ADDITIONAL WORDS AND PHRASES.         The Appendices comprise a Pronouncing Gazetteer of the World,
Vocabularies of Scripture, Greek, Latin, and English Proper
